'''Melanie Bruce''' (born 22 January 1972 in [[London]]) was an [[England|English]] [[ice dancer]].  With partner [[Andrew Place]], she won the gold medal at the 1990 [[British Figure Skating Championships]].  They finished 17th at the [[1992 European Figure Skating Championships]], 17th at the [[1992 Winter Olympics]], and 19th at the [[1992 World Figure Skating Championships]].

